# AgeRangeService.Error.invalidRequest

**Case**

Indicates your request contains invalid parameters or configuration.

## Declaration

```swift
case invalidRequest
```

## Interpreting error responses

- **AgeRangeService.Error.notAvailable**: Indicates the system was unable to share the person’s age range.
